#: ../../source/basic/next-steps.rst:3 24cb45b3521d48549b4f75040264b4e1
msgid "Next Steps"
msgstr "下一步"

#: ../../source/basic/next-steps.rst:5 84caa582776849a28214eb21886eaec6
msgid "These basic first steps should have gotten you started with the library."
msgstr "这些基本的初始步骤应该已经帮助您初步熟悉这个库。"

#: ../../source/basic/next-steps.rst:7 b84d36fb220e4c658e0500c3bceada51
msgid ""
"By now, you should know how to call friendly methods and how to work with"
" the returned objects, how things work inside event handlers, etc."
msgstr ""
"到目前为止，你应该已经掌握了如何调用友好的方法、如何处理返回的对象，"
"并了解了事件处理器内部如何工作等等相关内容了。"

#: ../../source/basic/next-steps.rst:10 096ab75f288f4c8a8f0dcf454b86f667
msgid ""
"Next, we will see a quick reference summary of *all* the methods and "
"properties that you will need when using the library. If you follow the "
"links there, you will expand the documentation for the method and "
"property, with more examples on how to use them."
msgstr ""
"接下来，你将看到一份关于该库中*所有*您在使用时会用到的方法和属性的快速参考摘要。"
"如果你点击其中的链接，您将能够查看该方法和属性的详细文档，"
"并会获得更多关于如何使用它们的示例。"

#: ../../source/basic/next-steps.rst:15 62be5b44cc3a435e975bf79abbc35569
msgid ""
"Therefore, **you can find an example on every method** of the client to "
"learn how to use it, as well as a description of all the arguments."
msgstr ""
"因此，**在客户端的每一个方法中**，您都能找到示例来学习如何使用该方法，"
"同时还能了解到所有参数的说明。"

#: ../../source/basic/next-steps.rst:18 5da35cfaf77046fc967f53161a7bd2e1
msgid ""
"After that, we will go in-depth with some other important concepts that "
"are worth learning and understanding."
msgstr ""
"然后，我们将深入探讨一些其他重要的概念，这些概念值得我们去学习和理解。"

#: ../../source/basic/next-steps.rst:21 88e824009bdd47d1aeb553d6f27691d9
msgid ""
"From now on, you can keep pressing the \"Next\" button if you want, or "
"use the menu on the left, since some pages are quite lengthy."
msgstr ""
"如果你愿意的话，可以一直点击 \"下一页\" 按钮，"
"或者使用左侧的菜单，因为有些页面内容相当长。"

#: ../../source/basic/next-steps.rst:25 54cea8049b12450b812ed0ad2d264c56
msgid "A note on developing applications"
msgstr "关于开发应用程序的一些说明"

#: ../../source/basic/next-steps.rst:27 93b571082b96438e81cf231316b7c165
msgid ""
"If you're using the library to make an actual application (and not just "
"automate things), you should make sure to `comply with the ToS <https://core.telegram.org/api/config#terms-of-service>`_:"
msgstr "如果您是利用这个库来开发实际的应用程序（而非仅仅用于自动化操作），"
"那么您应当确保 `遵守Telegram的相关服务条款 <https://core.telegram.org/api/config#terms-of-service>`_："

#: ../../source/basic/next-steps.rst:30 481aa42121e64db7b8b3a1d6a9781667
msgid ""
"[…] when logging in as an existing user, apps are supposed to call "
":tl:`GetTermsOfServiceUpdate` to check for any "
"updates to the Terms of Service; this call should be repeated after "
"``expires`` seconds have elapsed. If an update to the Terms Of Service is"
" available, clients are supposed to show a consent popup; if accepted, "
"clients should call :tl:`AcceptTermsOfService`, providing the "
"``termsOfService id`` JSON object; in case of denial, clients are to "
"delete the account using :tl:`DeleteAccount`,"
"providing Decline ToS update as deletion reason."
msgstr ""
"[…] 当以现有用户身份登录时，应用程序应调用 :tl:`GetTermsOfServiceUpdate` "
"来检查服务条款是否有任何更新；在 ``expires`` 秒数过后，应再次执行此调用。"
"如果服务条款有更新可用，客户端应显示同意弹窗；如果用户接受，客户端应调用 :tl:`AcceptTermsOfService`"
"，并提供 ``termsOfService id`` JSON 对象；如果拒绝，客户端应调用 :tl:`DeleteAccount` 删除账户，"
"并提供“拒绝服务条款更新”作为删除原因。"

#: ../../source/basic/next-steps.rst:41 871d29ca3bd34e12bf9926f25ff1fbbc
msgid ""
"However, if you use the library to automate or enhance your Telegram "
"experience, it's very likely that you are using other applications doing "
"this check for you (so you wouldn't run the risk of violating the ToS)."
msgstr ""
"然而，如果您使用该库来实现对 Telegram 使用体验的自动化或优化，"
"那么很有可能有其他应用程序在为您执行这项检查"
"（这样您就不会有违反服务条款的风险了）。"

#: ../../source/basic/next-steps.rst:45 a779673df75b4c60be159756eac4d892
msgid ""
"The library itself will not automatically perform this check or accept "
"the ToS because it should require user action."
msgstr ""
"库本身不会自动进行这项检查或接受服务条款，"
"因为这需要用户主动操作。"
